Subject: Updates are not applied
Description:
Backend Security Updates: Updates are not applied

Also EPP Software Update scheduled but not installed:
Product Maintenance - Netwrix Endpoint Protector 5.9.4.1 Focuses on Security, Manageability, and User Experience. (HWA-EPP4-U0066)
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c:
Apply backend update from Dashboard > Live update.
It mentions that it applies the update but it does not do it.
What_We_Know__c: The Epp server was not able to reach the ubuntu keysererver for the backend update.
Solution_Comment__c: Applied the key manually then ran the update command from the UI.
